Key Match Events: Mookie Betts hit a walk-off home run in the 9th inning
Shohei Ohtani hit another home run and collected two stolen bases
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Dodgers maintained their one-game lead over the Philadelphia Phillies atop the National League standings
Yoshinobu Yamamoto's outing marked only the third time he failed to see north of four innings across 17 starts in 2024
Shohei Ohtani is close to joining the 60-60 club with 53 home runs and 55 stolen bases
Others: The Dodgers will face the San Diego Padres and the Rockies again in a pair of three-game sets to end the 2024 campaign
